# Writing endpoints

When this rule applies, read and follow [`.cursor/skills/writing-endpoints/SKILL.md`](../skills/writing-endpoints/SKILL.md) **before** editing.

- HTTP params use **string keys only**; no atom-key fallbacks in controllers or contexts called from controllers.
- Keep controllers thin; register routes with the correct auth pipeline.
- HTML markup lives in `*_html.ex` with inline `~H"""` — **no** `.heex` files or `embed_templates`.
- Add or update ConnCase controller tests; run `mix test` on affected files before finishing.
